\c 37
\s Mwari anoonekwa pamabasa ake makuru sepakutinhira nemheni
\p
\v 1 Uye nekuda kweizvi moyo wangu unobvunda uye unouruka kubva panzvimbo yawo.
\v 2 Inzwa zvekunzwa mutinhiro weinzwi rake, hongu ruzha rwunobva mumuromo make rwunobuda.
\v 3 Anousunungura pasi pematenga ese, nechiedza chake pamusoro pemigumo yenyika.
\v 4 Shure kweizvi kunoomba inzwi; anotinhira neinzwi reukuru hwake; uye haazvidzivisi panonzwikwa inzwi rake.
\v 5 Mwari anotinhira nenzwi rake zvinoshamisa kwazvo; anoita zvinhu zvikuru zvatisinganzwisisi.
\v 6 Nokuti anoti kumagada echando: Chivai panyika; saizvozvo \add ku\add*mvura yekupfunha, uye \add ku\add*mvura huru yekupfunha yesimba rake.
\v 7 Anonamatidza ruoko rwemunhu umwe neumwe, kuti vazive vanhu vese vebasa rake.
\v 8 Zvino mhuka dzinopinda mumagara ndokurambira mumapako adzo.
\v 9 Dutu remhepo rinobuda pakamuri, nechando kumhepo dzekumaodzanyemba.
\v 10 Chando chakachena chinopiwa nemweya waMwari, uye mvura mhamhi inogwamba.
\v 11 Hongu, neunyoro anozadza gore; anoparadzira gore nekupenya kwake.
\v 12 Uye iro rinotenderera kupotedza nekururamisa kwake\x + Zvir. 1.5. 11.14. 12.5. 20.18. 24.6.\x*, kuti zviite zvese zvaanozviraira\x + Map. 148.8.\x* pamusoro pechiso chevhu repanyika\x + 34.13. Zvir. 8.31. Map. 90.2.\x*.
\v 13 Anozvisvikisa\x + 2 Sam. 21.10. 1 Madz. 18.45.\x* kungava neshamhu\x + 36.31. 38.23. 1 Sam. 12.18,19. Ezi. 10.9.\x*, kungava nenyika yake\x + 38.26,27.\x*, kungava netsitsi.
\p
\v 14 Teerera kune izvi, Jobho; mira, ugorangarira mabasa anoshamisa aMwari\x + 31.1.\x*.
\v 15 Unoziva here kuti Mwari anoagadzira rinhi, apenyese chiedza chegore rake\x + 37.11.\x*?
\v 16 Unoziva here kuremberedzwa kwemakore, zvishamiso zvewakaperera\x + 36.4. 1 Sam. 2.3.\x* paruzivo\x + 32.6.\x*?
\v 17 Kuti nguvo dzako dzinodziya sei, pakunyaradza kwenyika nemhepo yekuchamhembe\x + Det. 33.23.\x*?
\v 18 Wakaradanura here gore pamwe naye\x + Gen.. 1.6. Isa. 44.24.\x*, asimbe sechionioni chakaumbwa nekunyunguduswa\x + 38.38. Eki. 24.10.\x*?
\p
\v 19 Tidzidzise zvatichareva kwaari; hatingagadziri \add chinhu\add* nekuda\x + 17.12. 23.17.\x* kwerima\x + Isa. 60.2. VaEfe. 4.18.\x*.
\v 20 Zvingatsanangurwa kwaari here kuti ndinotaura? Kana munhu akataura, zvirokwazvo achamedzwa\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino ikozvino havaoni chiedza chinopenya chiri mumakore, mhepo painopfuura inoachenesa\x + 31.26.\x*.
\v 22 Goridhe rinobva kuchamhembe. Kuna Mwari kune umambo hunotyisa\x + Map. 104.1.\x*.
\v 23 Wemasimbaose hatimuwani\x + 1 Tim. 6.16.\x*; mukuru pasimba\x + 36.5.\x* nepamutongo; uye mukuru pakururama; haamanikidzi\x + Map. 99.4.\x*.
\v 24 Naizvozvo vanhu\x + 36.24.\x* vanomutya\x + Mat. 10.28.\x*; haatarisi\x + Det. 33.9.\x* vakachenjera\x + Mat. 11.25. Isa. 5.21.\x* pamoyo\x + 34.10.\x*.